; This has been extracted from
; https://github.com/tldr-pages/tldr/blob/master/pages/windows/msaccess.md

% msaccess, windows

# Launch the database application
msaccess

# Open an existing database file
msaccess <path_to_file_accdb>

# Open an existing database file in [r]ead-[o]nly mode
msaccess /ro <path_to_fileaccdb>

# Open a database, then e[x]ecute a specific macro
msaccess <path_to_file_accdb> /x <MacroName>
